        {
            "text": "The Dalitz-plot of the D 0 \u2192 \u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 \u03c0 0 decay. ",
            "section": "DATA COLLECTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 8,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "s + and s \u2212 are respectively m 2 (\u03c0 + \u03c0 0 ) and m 2 (\u03c0 \u2212 \u03c0 0 ). ",
