            "paragraph_rank": 8,
            "section_rank": 3
        },
        {
            "text": "The fine diagonal line at low \u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 mass corresponds to the events removed by the cut 489 < M(\u03c0 + \u03c0 \u2212 ) < 508 MeV/c 2 . ",
            "section": "DATA COLLECTION",
            "paragraph_rank": 8,
            "section_rank": 3
